Lelo nolonga na mweye wanhu weli siyo Wayahudi. Kwaviya niye ni mtumigwa kwa wanhu weli siyo Wayahudi, nowena vinogile sang'hano yangu.
Ndangugana niwatende wanhu wayangu waniwonele migongo, muladi niwakombole wamwenga wawo.
Kwaviya kwaviya kwaviya walekeligwa, Mulungu kawahanyisa wanhu nayo, vilihi vondayahakundigwe, wanhu wadanganike wezazilibuka?
