Vino lelo loleni, Mulungu kowatendela vihile kwa kunoga, hebu viyowatenda vihile wanhu wagwile, mbali iyo kana unovu kumwenu mweye one muhakala muna unovu wake, mbali one hamutendile ivo, na mweye iviya mwizadumigwa.
