Iviya na wawo sambi walema kumuhulika Mulungu, muladi wawo iviya wabochele ubazi wa Mulungu, kwa ichimu cha ubazi uwo womuwonele mweye.
Kwaviya Mulungu kawaguma wanhu wose muna dilema da kuleka kumuhulika Mulungu muladi yawonele ubazi wose.
