Kwa unovu wa Mulungu woyaninile, nomulongelani mweye wose, chila munhu sekeyewone mwenyewo kuwa mkulu kufosa viyolondeka yawe, mbali yavimanye kuwa na nzewele zinoga fana Mulungu viyamwing'hile chila munhu uhuwilo wake.
Kwaviya muna lukuli lumwe muna diwalo nyingi, na chila chitomo chochitenda sang'hano yake.
